{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/07/01/海南省博物馆.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"47364007-c95b-53f6-bd1b-42269a8ebffc","excerpt":"…","html":"<h1>海南省博物馆</h1>\n<p>刚到海口的旅店，就发现门口的大树上面生了一颗波罗蜜。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/c84e8/01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.43243243243244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/cbe2e/01.webp 148w,\n/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/3084c/01.webp 295w,\n/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/5ca24/01.webp 590w,\n/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/53666/01.webp 743w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/a80bd/01.jpg 148w,\n/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/1c91a/01.jpg 295w,\n/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/1c72d/01.jpg 590w,\n/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/c84e8/01.jpg 743w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/92330c47733b38529958666bdd45da6e/1c72d/01.jpg\"\n          alt=\"门口的波罗蜜\"\n          title=\"门口的波罗蜜\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">门口的波罗蜜</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>海南博物馆附近有一家「老姐情怀」，顺便体验一下，芒果肠粉很好吃，糟粕醋就是一种粉，个人感觉不怎么好吃。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/72e01/02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/cbe2e/02.webp 148w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/3084c/02.webp 295w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/5ca24/02.webp 590w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/dad35/02.webp 885w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/a9a89/02.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/a80bd/02.jpg 148w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/1c91a/02.jpg 295w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/1c72d/02.jpg 590w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/a8a14/02.jpg 885w,\n/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/72e01/02.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/f4bce65b351ebd52d34aeb682de24058/1c72d/02.jpg\"\n          alt=\"芒果肠粉和糟粕醋\"\n          title=\"芒果肠粉和糟粕醋\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">芒果肠粉和糟粕醋</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>海南博物馆很大，貌似是有一部分介绍海南人文饮食和产物的老馆和介绍南海以及南海历史的新馆组成，新老馆的差距很明显，新馆有空调。</p>\n<p>老馆关于沉香的制作过程很详细，那么大一棵树，最后只能做那么一点沉香我也是惊了。新馆声电做的很震撼，也很吓人。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/72e01/03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/cbe2e/03.webp 148w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/3084c/03.webp 295w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/5ca24/03.webp 590w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/dad35/03.webp 885w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/a9a89/03.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/a80bd/03.jpg 148w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/1c91a/03.jpg 295w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/1c72d/03.jpg 590w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/a8a14/03.jpg 885w,\n/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/72e01/03.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/a133932e9295a92ce296bcfc7c7a4809/1c72d/03.jpg\"\n          alt=\"博物馆里的民国街\"\n          title=\"博物馆里的民国街\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">博物馆里的民国街</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>博物馆力荐一种清补凉，叫鸡屎藤。是使用一种鸡失藤的野菜榨汁拧成细条放到椰汁里面，在骑楼街体验了一下，没啥特别的(ˉ▽ˉ；)…</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/72e01/04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/cbe2e/04.webp 148w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/3084c/04.webp 295w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/5ca24/04.webp 590w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/dad35/04.webp 885w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/a9a89/04.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/a80bd/04.jpg 148w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/1c91a/04.jpg 295w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/1c72d/04.jpg 590w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/a8a14/04.jpg 885w,\n/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/72e01/04.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/248fa6efb20df4696843433b93ca8d12/1c72d/04.jpg\"\n          alt=\"骑楼街\"\n          title=\"骑楼街\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">骑楼街</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>骑楼街是海口第一的景点，是以中山路为中心的东南亚风格的骑楼群。这种建筑在厦门、汕头、广州等都很常见，也基本都叫中山路。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/72e01/05.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/cbe2e/05.webp 148w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/3084c/05.webp 295w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/5ca24/05.webp 590w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/dad35/05.webp 885w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/a9a89/05.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/a80bd/05.jpg 148w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/1c91a/05.jpg 295w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/1c72d/05.jpg 590w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/a8a14/05.jpg 885w,\n/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/72e01/05.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/b0eca136b60374cceff8db54c327e5c9/1c72d/05.jpg\"\n          alt=\"人民路\"\n          title=\"人民路\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">人民路</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>因为住在美兰，从海口去美兰大概 7 分钟的环岛车程。票价也是 7 块。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/72e01/06.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.94594594594595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/cbe2e/06.webp 148w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/3084c/06.webp 295w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/5ca24/06.webp 590w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/dad35/06.webp 885w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/a9a89/06.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/a80bd/06.jpg 148w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/1c91a/06.jpg 295w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/1c72d/06.jpg 590w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/a8a14/06.jpg 885w,\n/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/72e01/06.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/cf401d1ce0db3a1a4498dea98aeebffe/1c72d/06.jpg\"\n          alt=\"随处可见的椰树牌椰汁的广告\"\n          title=\"随处可见的椰树牌椰汁的广告\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">随处可见的椰树牌椰汁的广告</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/01/海南省博物馆.html","date":"July 01, 2020","title":"海南省博物馆"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/01/海南省博物馆.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2020/06/30/隐秘的角落.html","title":"隐秘的角落"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tv"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2020/07/03/暗黑.html","title":"暗黑"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tv"}}}}}